6 F. If within thirty (30) days of the delivery of a written
7 rental agreement from the owner to the occupant by hand delivery,
8 first-class mail, or, if mutually agreed between the owner and
9 occupant in the rental agreement or in an addendum to the rental
10 agreement, by electronic mail, the occupant fails to sign such
11 rental agreement, the occupant's payment of rent or continued use of
12 the storage space shall be deemed an acceptance of the rental
13 agreement and such rental agreement shall be enforceable against the
14 occupant as if it had been signed by the occupant.
